The cover is also removable and washable. NO HOT SEAT ANYMORE - This ventilated gel cushion has been designed to maintain proper temperature. With an air mesh cover that is breathable and washable it allows a maximum amount of air flow through the cushion. Forget about the heat and the irritation from previous experience. This cushion certainly will make a difference. RELIEF PAIN - It is difficult for people with back pain to sit with comfort. This cushion is designed to relieve the pain from lumbar, hip, tailbone and coccyx. The high quality gel hugs tailbone and maintains its shape and contour without compromising the comfort. Study shows people with back pain are able to sit longer period of time with this cushion than any other leading brand on the market today.

Fantastic - You Can Sit on an Egg! Your achy spine and backside on our Gel Seat Cushion, the support cushion that supports so well that you can sit on an egg without breaking it. Say goodbye to sore, stiff muscles caused by sitting all day or long car rides. Standard support cushions need a hole cut out of the cushion to support your tailbone. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wow, so comfortable!
reviews.reviewText: I recently broke my pelvis, and I couldn’t sit anywhere because of the pain. Once I received the cushion, it was like a miracle, everywhere I placed the cushion, I was painless and comfy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great cushion and a good price!
reviews.reviewText: I like the thickness of this cushion and the cover that goes with it has good grip so it doesn't sliparound on the chair. I would recommmend it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Anti slip backing....
reviews.reviewText: Orginally bought to relive pressure sores for an elderly patient. It was actually used at the patients chair at the table. The gel cushioning is nice for a comfortable sit and the backing has anti slip nubs that keep the cushion in place. The elderly really need both these features, but hey, who doesn't ?!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Small and thin.
reviews.reviewText: When I go to restaurants and have to sit in wooden chairs I find it very uncomfortable especially since I've lost a lot of weight. I will keep this cousion but it is very thin and narrow. I think it will serve my purpose but would not recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Larger than others on Amazon
reviews.reviewText: I particularly like this one best. It is larger & the edges are firm & don't breakdown at all when setting on it.I use it for my office chair and then I take it in my car and it is perfect. It keeps me from having so much pain getting in and out of the car and getting up for my desk chair. I can walk right away without pain. (As opposed to traveling for the first 5 or 6 feet before I can straighten up.)I know if my mom was still alive, She would have loved this cushion, I highly recommend this.It has a zip off cover. And so far, there's no dirt on it from even being transported back-and-forth. I think is well worth the price... And it came in 2 days!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Incredible! It's just as good as they say!
reviews.reviewText: I suffer from chronic back pain and I'm in a wheelchair I use at home / scooter while out. I usually started to really hurt 10-15 mins after sitting in it.Now most Dr appts take much longer and by the time I got home I was in agony.To say this makes a difference in my life is an understatement. You see, even my motorized wheelchair in the home which has a nice comfy seat, after about 30 mins the pain was horrendous but then sciatica would jump in.Since I started using this I can sit for I don't know how long in my wheelchair. It's longer than before and my trips to Dr appts are so much better. I never mentioned how much better my butt feels! Wow! I'm not constantly repositioning myself. Thank you to the makers of this great pillow!If you have a family member who suffers sitting, they would probably live this under the tree!No I'm not being paid, I'm just giving my honest opinion.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars I should have kept it
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to use for long drives which didn't work for my car seat.I'm sure on a hard chair seat the exact same dimensions it would be comfortable. I have sciatica for which is difficult to find relief with much of any aid product. 🤔

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought the super large gel cushion for my mom because she had a small pressure sore from sitting. She says it's very comfortable and did help relieve the pain. Measurements stated 19" x 18" but it is a little short by about an inch each way. It's still a great buy because it seemed to help her problem. Has had it about a month and seems to be holding up good. Would recommend.
